Assist, i Uddevalla 27-28, vik. i Vara 28-29, egen praktik i UddevaHa sed. 29. Skattmäst. i Bohusl. tandl:-säMisk. 34-36, v. ordf. sed. 37. Hobby: fiske.
translated: Frankenberg, Gunnar Daniel, dentist, born on October 9, 1905 in Uddevalla to Oscar F. and Sigrid Sofia Ekstrand. Married to Britta Meligren in 1930. Children: Sten-Gunnar (born in 1931), Birgitta (born in 1935, deceased in 1940), Lars (born in 1941), Karin (born in 1942). Completed high school in Uddevalla in 1924, graduated from dental school in 1925 and became a licensed dentist in 1927. Worked as an assistant in Uddevalla from 1927-1928, a substitute in Vara from 1928-1929, and ran his own practice in Uddevalla afterwards. Served as treasurer in the Bohuslän Dental Society from 1934-1936, and as vice chairperson from 1937 onwards. His hobby was fishing.
